ts with missed/late payments).\",\n","    \"CLAGE\":   \"Age of the applicant's oldest credit line, in months — longer history signals a more established borrower.\",\n","    \"NINQ\":    \"Number of recent credit inquiries — frequent inquiries can indicate active credit-seeking / financial stress.\",\n","    \"CLNO\":    \"Total number of credit lines the applicant holds.\",\n","    \"DEBTINC\": \"Debt-to-income ratio — monthly debt obligations divided by monthly income. Higher = more stretched.\",\n","}\n","\n","with open(f\"{base}/model/column_descriptions.json\", \"w\") as f:\n","    json.dump(column_descriptions, f, indent=2)\n","print(\"saved column_descriptions.json\")"],"metadata":{"colab":{"base_uri":"https://localhost:8080/"},"id":"HIGvcvpNaqL9","executionInfo":{"status":"ok","timestamp":1783492247260,"user_tz":-330,"elapsed":93,"user":{"displayName":"Abhinav Barman 4-Yr B.Tech.: Civil Engg., IIT(BHU)","userId":"02235557058045586589"}},"outputId":"8779a840-1762-4e05-b68c-9df1f74d337b"},"execution_count":20,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":["saved column_descriptions.json\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":[],"metadata":{"id":"PXWMI97la_yi"},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]}]}